movie.title: Alive
movie.plot: The amazing, true story of a Uruguayan rugby team's plane that crashed in the middle of the Andes mountains, and their immense will to survive and pull through alive, forced to do anything and everything they could to stay alive on meager rations and through the freezing cold.
movie.awards: Nominated for 1 Primetime Emmy. Another 1 win & 1 nomination.
